Scirus’ coverage of purely sc ientific sources in addition to Elsevier's  ScienceDirect full-text collection is low by comp arison (compare the sele ction of hosts in the  Scirus advanced search interface, http://scirus.com/srsapp/advanced/).

The original system CiteSeer (http://citeseer.ist.psu.edu/) as well as Google Scholar have  up to now implemented only  heuristics for the application of ACI that also produce some errors in the citation values  (see  also Jacsó, 2005c; 2006a; 2006b).
